{"tid":1126457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿小學時曾被老師罵「廢紙」 廿三歲男返母校以銀紙摑恩師臉","createTime":"2019-04-26T11:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T17:07:45.000Z","uid":133680,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bfaa770d2c665c676ec3510157a6936dfeb0e1fb","tid":1126457,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E3%80%8D-%E8%BF%94%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E6%91%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%87%89-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25B6%25E6%258F%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E7%25B4%2599%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2588%2594%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2591%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2587%2589-23%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3Tjtw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=198b7f37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25B6%25E6%258F%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E7%25B4%2599%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2588%2594%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2591%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2587%2589-23%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA&h=439aaed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E3%80%8D-%E8%BF%94%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E6%91%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%87%89-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n23歲男子稱讀小學時不滿被老師比喻為「回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」，一直耿耿於懷，去年重返母校外斥責該老師，更兩度用鈔票摑打對方臉孔。男生今在西九龍裁判法院承認一項「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」，被判以自簽2000元守行為1年，並賠償事主1000元、支付300元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報稱任金融經紀的被告莊洋洋（23歲）今承認，去年9月20日在葵涌慈幼葉漢小學外襲擊李家偉，對對方造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官聽畢案情後曾問被告，為何用鈔票拍打別人臉部。被告回應稱，「佢（案中事主）比喻我係回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」。裁判官聞言表示，一個人是否受人尊重，不是視乎掙多少錢，又形容被告「咁樣做好侮辱」。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告讀小學時，曾因學業不佳被事主懲罰，令他耿耿於懷。至去年9月，被告在母校外情緒激動斥責事主，並用胸口撞撃事主3次，更從銀包取出11張港元和人民幣鈔票，兩度用鈔票摑打事主臉孔。被告又用手兩度抓住事主的衣領，導致對方頸部輕微擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n事主其他同事見狀報警，被告在警誡下表示「我只係同佢嘈，我冇打過佢」，到其後在錄影會面時指出，自己小學時因學業不佳遭事主懲罰，故透過撞撃及用鈔票摑打對方，來表達不滿。"},{"pid":"07ce2ce8758116aaeb3388de203d00834859a48f","tid":1126457,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71cb20a193dcefe5556bf553786878af1dd2bda","tid":1126457,"uid":156144,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"邊忽恩師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76505d0b27f8fbb7089e0c0097fab500de2cb61e","tid":1126457,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"快啲攞一千蚊紙打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf18384a2a5b6afb9b8e00d41a741f236ee05ad","tid":11264